text:
Ah, this group, huh? They've been getting a lot
of TV appearances since around last week.

Apparently their popularity has been spreading like wildfire by
word of mouth. Or at least that's what I learned from the briefing.

Well... they did just debut afterall.
But they've definitely got the potential────

...It's this part of you that thinks Fuyu doesn't know something
as obvious as this that gets to me, you know.

Eh.... Ah, sorry!
I honestly though you might not know...

Make sure you do your research properly, okay?
......about Fuyu♡
